dssqlddl: CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW CRMVPIPELINELEAD AS SELECT a.BAJA as BAJA,a.DEFECTO as DEFECTO,a.IDXCRMPIPELINE as IDXCRMPIPELINE,a.MAXREG as MAXREG,a.MODULO as MODULO,a.ORDENASC as ORDENASC,a.PIPELINE as PIPELINE FROM CRMPIPELINE a WHERE   BAJA= false AND  UPPER (MODULO) LIKE upper('%crmoportunidad%');
